name: vs2015-dark-syntax

1.0.10.name: VS2015-dark-syntax
1.0.10.description: Dark syntax theme based on visual studio 2015 community edition dark
1.0.10.readme:
# VS2015-dark-syntax theme

This dark syntax theme is based on visual studio 2015 community edition dark theme. I would recommend using a UI theme based around visual studio and using Consolas as the font.

## Screenshots
#### HTML

![HTML](http://icesentry.net/sharex/atom_2016-03-08_10-56-39.png)

#### Javascript

![Javascript](http://icesentry.net/sharex/atom_2016-03-08_10-57-26.png)

#### CSS

![CSS](http://icesentry.net/sharex/atom_2016-03-08_10-58-33.png)

#### LESS

![LESS](http://icesentry.net/sharex/atom_2016-03-08_10-59-35.png)

All the examples are taken from the Meteor.js tutorial page. Ass you can also see the theme supports handlebars used in meteor, but you will need the meteor-api package for it to work properly.
